        public abstract ValueT put(KeyT k,
                           ValueT v,
                           DropEvent<KeyT,ValueT> fsop,
                           EvictFilter<KeyT,ValueT> dfilter)
        Put an entry in this cache pool and evict eldest entries if necessary that will free enough space to hold new entry, which entry could be evicted that can be customized by (EvictFilter), regarding how to post-process the eldest entry that can be customized by ( DropEvent). If this cache pool previously contained an entry for the key, the old value will be replaced by the specified value
        Parameters:
        k - the key whoes associated value is to be put
        v - the value to be put
        fsop - the customized operations to free space to hold new entry
        dfilter - the filter of entries for deletion
        Returns:
        true if the entry has been put into this container
